.TH "drm_atomic_helper_update_plane" 9 "drm_atomic_helper_update_plane" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_atomic_helper_update_plane \- Helper for primary plane update using atomic
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" drm_atomic_helper_update_plane
.BI "(struct drm_plane *plane "  ","
.BI "struct drm_crtc *crtc "  ","
.BI "struct drm_framebuffer *fb "  ","
.BI "int crtc_x "  ","
.BI "int crtc_y "  ","
.BI "unsigned int crtc_w "  ","
.BI "unsigned int crtc_h "  ","
.BI "uint32_t src_x "  ","
.BI "uint32_t src_y "  ","
.BI "uint32_t src_w "  ","
.BI "uint32_t src_h "  ","
.BI "struct drm_modeset_acquire_ctx *ctx "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "plane" 12
plane object to update
.IP "crtc" 12
owning CRTC of owning plane
.IP "fb" 12
framebuffer to flip onto plane
.IP "crtc_x" 12
x offset of primary plane on \fIcrtc\fP
.IP "crtc_y" 12
y offset of primary plane on \fIcrtc\fP
.IP "crtc_w" 12
width of primary plane rectangle on \fIcrtc\fP
.IP "crtc_h" 12
height of primary plane rectangle on \fIcrtc\fP
.IP "src_x" 12
x offset of \fIfb\fP for panning
.IP "src_y" 12
y offset of \fIfb\fP for panning
.IP "src_w" 12
width of source rectangle in \fIfb\fP
.IP "src_h" 12
height of source rectangle in \fIfb\fP
.IP "ctx" 12
lock acquire context
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Provides a default plane update handler using the atomic driver interface.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success, error code on failure
